          </details>
          <details class="faq-item">
            <summary>I'm hauling out of the Port of Philadelphia. Any special requirements?</summary>
            <p>Port work may require additional coverage depending on your cargo. Refrigerated loads have special weight permits (up to 107,500 lbs in the Philadelphia area). We know PhilaPort operations and will make sure your coverage matches what the terminals and brokers require.</p>
          </details>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

